#

Seared Duck Breast with Cherry Gastrique

$25
750 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-Free

Tags:

GourmetDinnerDate Night

Description

Succulent seared duck breast with a rich cherry gastrique, served atop a creamy butternut squash puree.

Ingredients

  • Duck Breasts: 2
  • Cherries: 1 cup
  • Sugar: 1/2 cup
  • Red Wine Vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • Butternut Squash: 1 medium
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Heavy Cream: 1/4 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
